Class Trace<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.numenta.nupic.monitor.mixin.Trace<T>

    BoolsTrace, CountsTrace, IndicesTrace, MetricsTrace, StringsTrace

    public abstract class Trace<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A record of the past data the algorithm has seen, with an entry for each iteration. Contains Trace classes used in monitor mixin framework.
    Author:
    Chetan Surpur, cogmission
